*   **(R1) 64-bit signed IDs:** Handled by `long` and string-serialization in snapshots.
*   **(R2) Out-of-order:** `tombstone(id)` can be called for an ID that hasn't arrived yet. The `tombstonedIds.add(id)` line ensures that when the event eventually arrives via `append`, it is immediately blocked.
